---
title: Quick BBQ Prawns & Slaw Tacos with Cheddar Cheese & Plant-Based Mayo
description: It’s a good day when you’re having tacos for dinner. Let’s pack these tortillas with as much All-American spiced peeled prawns as possible, tossed with baby leaves and a colourful slaw on top. Don’t forget the Cheddar cheese!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66cfd30185e4e45d54640c01-c19228d7.jpeg
